sections.heading: Order; award; judgment; use of terms
sections.text: Except as otherwise provided in sections 48-192 to 48-1,109, the words order, award, and judgment, as used in the Nebraska Workers' Compensation Act, are used interchangeably and are deemed to have the same meaning.SourceLaws 1935, c. 57, ยง 12, p. 192;C.S.Supp.,1
